Package com.example.mobilibrary.Activity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LogIn
    LogIn activity lets user log into the app with their unique email registered to Firebase Authentication User can also choose to go to SignUp activity to create a new account.
    ProfileActivity
    This class displays a user's profile (username, email, and phone number), and if the viewer is also the currently logged in user, allows editing of the email and phone number (with re-authentication).
    SignUp
    SignUp activity allows new user to create new account User can go back to LogIn screen by clicking on the back button on toolbar
    StartActivity
    This is the activity seen when the app is first opened, containing the log in/sign up options.
